            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="meta-taskdescription" metaValue="Manage tax fixed asset reporting&#10;Here are the BOBJ reports:&#10;Asset List HANA (F60), &#10;Asset List Webi on HANA (F61)&#10;Asset Retirements HANA (F67),&#10;Tax Cost Roll Forward (F73),&#10;Tax Depreciation Roll Forward (F74),&#10;Tax Roll Forward (F75)&#10;New reports (to be built): &#10;Report to reconcile cost basis between GAAP and Tax,&#10;AUC depreciation forecast,&#10;CAPEX depreciation forecast (SAC)&#10;&#10;"/>
